{Thrash}

    The tiny one transformer shuttle skimmed earths atmosphere, c=
utting through the upper clouds like a sharpened disc as it descended lower=
 and lower eventually coming into the visible skies like a flaming comet be=
fore hurtling down into the ocean.

    As the craft begins to shake itself=
 apart, a life form scanning device emerges from a slot emitting both a sca=
n and a locational beacon on all frequencies, even as the beacon sends out =
its continual message the scan stops. Moments pass before the shuttles wind=
 shield bursts from the shuttle, a giant great white shark knifing out into=
 the waters...
